<plot>Through the eyes of Autism is a short film that shows an autistic child's world through visual imagery, music, sound effects, and text. This film uses different attributes of autism as chapters. The film is entirely through the child's point of view and uses typical childhood settings like school, the playground, and home to show their world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?606414</url></doc>
